    note right of Dragging
        addDragSourceListener() throws TooManyListenersException
        if a listener is already registered.
        Constructor dsl param may be null (no listener added).
    end note

    note right of DraggingWithListener
        addDragSourceListener() is forbidden in this state.
        Listener was registered either via constructor (non-null dsl)
        or via addDragSourceListener().
    end note

    note right of Ended
        Terminal state after dragDropEnd() is called.
        The drag-and-drop operation has completed.
    end note
